article_title: Walker Trumps The GOP Presidential Field In Healthcare Reform

article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes

og.description: Wisconsin Governor Scott Walker has come out with the first viable and serious healthcare reform plan from the GOP presidential hopefuls. It's worth taking seriously.
